    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为IoT工业MQTT代理的版本控制画一个Git流程图。关键是要展示main分支和develop分支之间的双向合并，这在我们的持续集成场景里很常见。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。您说的双向合并，是指develop合并到main之后，main再合并回develop，然后可能再循环一次？还是只要一次来回？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是来回两次。第一次develop合到main发布版本，然后main合回develop同步基线，最后develop再合到main做下一个迭代。这样能体现我们工业场景下的严谨流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先初始化gitGraph，方向设成LR横向布局。从main分支开始，第一个commit之后切出develop分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gitGraph LR",
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "develop上先做一个commit，然后切回main，把develop合并进来——这是第一次合并。接着main再做一个commit标记版本发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在develop合并到了main，main上有了新commit。接下来是main合并回develop对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，checkout到develop，merge main，然后develop再commit一次新功能，最后切回main做第二次merge develop。这样双向两次合并就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "checkout",
        "merge",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
